This commit along with github repository level
Actions setting enables some security for
self-hosted runners.

https://github.com/gshiva/pygptcourse/settings/actions

This addresses along with PR approval required for
workflow runs, the security issue listed here:

https://docs.github.com/en/actions/managing-workflow-runs/approving-workflow-runs-from-public-forks

With these the self-hosted runner at RPi
can be added.
